A woman showed off her incredible 94 pound weight loss after she was dumped and spent the next 18 months perfecting her “revenge body.” Influencer Dani Dragun regularly shares pictures and videos of her dramatic weight loss transformation. She shared that she decided to lose weight after being ditched by a fella and now hoped he’d be jealous of her stunning figure. In one video, she said: “He was hurting inside because he s****ed on me and finally got s****ed on. And imagine that!” Dani showed herself in 2019 when she was at her heaviest and then after when she had shed an incredible 88 pounds. She added the caption: “IMAGINE THAT !!! My 94 pound weight loss!!” Despite the spectacular change, Dani did confess that she doesn’t always feel great about her new shape. She explained that she still has loose skin following the weight loss. In a video she said: “If I lose all this weight I’ll stop hating myself and my body. Just know that if you hide, it doesn’t go away.” Fellow TikTokers flocked to asked for the savvy slimmer’s tips and she confirmed that she had been using Weight Watchers since January 2020. Referring to her ex boyfriend, one person said: “He’s balling his eyes out in the corner of the room. I just know it.” Another said: “I’m in love. I wanna be you!” A third said: “No ones gonna talk about you giving Kourtney K vibes?! Yes ma’am!!!” Heart-warmingly Dani’s mum took to TikTok to share her pride in her daughter: “This is my daughter. She doesn’t work out. Never has she had any skin removal surgery or a bbl… she got that from her mama!” This story originally appeared on The Sun and was reproduced here with permission.